name: Rolodex
tagline: a simple contacts viewer using Sproutcore
body:
# Rolodex
Rolodex - your contacts are on a roll...

## Features
* Sproutcore frontend, Rails backend.


## Submodules
Added Rails app 'contacts' datasource as a submodule using command:
git submodule add git@github.com:rupakg/contacts.git contacts
